column6: Every country employs covert superhumans to protect their interests. And while pursuing the foe who killed one of their own, X-Force is about to run afoul of the United Kingdom's superhuman operatives: PETE WISDOM and MI13! In this game of spy versus spy, how can X-Force manage to outplay the best spy there is?
column8: | editor:Daniel Ketchum | penciller:Rock-He Kim | writer:Simon Spurrier
